                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1603-offence-1 t18450818-cd-12"></join>17th of July</rs>, at Hendon, and stealing therein, 1 coat, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18450818-name-177" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-177" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
